---
title: Satay Tofu Noodle with Stir-Fry Greens
description: Fresh and light meet peanut-ty heaven in this tofu miracle! Ramen noodles bring together delicious carrot ribbons and bok choy all mixed together with a decadent homemade satay sauce. This dish brings all the yummy flavour of Thai takeout to your table faster than delivery!
